<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>قُلْ هُوَ اللَّهُ أَحَدٌ <span class="c2">(١)</span> اللَّهُ الصَّمَدُ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> لَمْ يَلِدْ وَلَمْ يُولَدْ <span class="c2">(٣)</span> وَلَمْ يَكُنْ لَهُ كُفُوًا أَحَدٌ <span class="c2">(٤)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>